1
00:00:02,305 --> 00:00:04,195
The boss would like a word
with you in his office Elena.

2
00:00:10,094 --> 00:00:12,257
Hi Elena. Our new star reporter.

3
00:00:12,344 --> 00:00:13,951
You are exagerrating.

4
00:00:13,976 --> 00:00:16,375
You probably already guessed
why I wanted to see you?

5
00:00:16,546 --> 00:00:18,085
No, I don`t. Why?

6
00:00:19,139 --> 00:00:21,724
You are now truly a big event
in profressional journalism.

7
00:00:22,109 --> 00:00:23,437
I have two possibilities now.

8
00:00:23,809 --> 00:00:25,957
Either we have to say goodbye

9
00:00:25,957 --> 00:00:28,400
and you take on a better
paid post somewhere else.

10
00:00:29,259 --> 00:00:30,978
No, I want to work here.

11
00:00:30,978 --> 00:00:32,431
That`s is what I`d hoped for.

12
00:00:32,916 --> 00:00:34,931
Then the second possibility
becomes reality.

13
00:00:34,931 --> 00:00:37,025
As you know I myself
will leave the newspaper soon.

14
00:00:37,478 --> 00:00:39,415
I wish to ask you
if you will be my successor.

15
00:00:39,556 --> 00:00:42,712
Elena Böhm,
I promote you to editor-in-chief.

16
00:00:44,229 --> 00:00:46,338
I am lost for words.

17
00:00:47,198 --> 00:00:50,843
Thank you. This is really a great honour.

18
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:52,520
Thanks

